beer.beer_description: Here’s hoping this one’s better than the last fucking one. We can’t make any promises, but we can get things off to a fucking good start. Fuck Yeah 2021, a lovely lazy hazy blend of light malt and oats, treated to a triple dose of aromatic hop extract, cryo hops, and hand selected Citra, Strata and Galaxy. Start off on a high note and fingers crossed.
